        display: grid;
        align-content: center;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-inline: auto;
        background-color: var(--color-bg);
        width: clamp(1rem, 5vw + 2rem, 8rem);
        height: 100px;
      }

      .square__text {
        color: var(--color-fg);
      } -->
  </body>
</html>
